race.comment: GEOSTORM (8) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 5 win two back (20.86) at this track. Has the ability and expected to bounce back. HIBIKI BLUE (1) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (21.19) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here.
